This directory contains three files.
1.Driver
2.Make File
3.User Application

Driver is running on kernel space
Makefile is used to build the kernel linux device driver
User application will running on the user space and communicate to driver on kernel space.

If you want to see the explanation of this driver, please visit below link.
http://www.embetronicx.com/tutorials/linux/device-drivers/linux-device-driver-tutorial-programming/
